data.text:
The Washington Space Business Roundtable (WSBR) will hold a luncheon on May 17, 2024 from 12:00-1:30 pm ET at Hogan Lovells, 555 13th St., NW, Washington, DC.

The speaker is Col. Richard Kniseley, Senior Materiel Leader of U.S. Space Force’s Space Systems Command’s Commercial Space Office.
